二、指定教科書及參考資料 Textbooks and Reference(請修課同學遵守智慧財產權，不得非法影印)


●指定教科書 Required Texts陳牧民、陳宛鬱，2012，圖解國際關係，臺北市:五南圖書。海伍德，2013，全球政治，臺北市:五南圖書。
		●參考書資料暨網路資源 Reference Books and Online Resources


三、教學目標 Objectives


This course is designed to provide an overview of international relations in the era of globalization for the first-year undergraduates. It will guide students to go through competing theoretical perspectives of international relations, understand political, economic, social, and cultural dimensions of globalization, and evaluate the resulting effects of globalization on domestic development and world politics. The course aims to enrich students’ knowledge of current issues and development of global politics and induce students to rethink whether globalization exists or not.　


